eewbot.scmd.help.title: Help
eewbot.scmd.help.desc:
Use slash commands.
Type `/` and select the bot's avatar to display a list of available commands.
eewbot.scmd.help.field.set.value: Sets the type of information and minimum seismic intensity that the bot will notify in the current channel. By default, Manage Server permission is required.
eewbot.scmd.help.field.time.value:
Checks the bot's time synchronization information.
Forced resynchronization is also available.
eewbot.scmd.help.field.invite.value: Obtains the invitation URL for the bot.
eewbot.scmd.help.field.testmessage.value: Send a test message from the bot to verify if it works correctly in the current channel.
eewbot.scmd.help.field.lang.value: Set the bot’s language. Requires manage server permission by default.
